{"tid":1583508,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【公投】何妖聽日會唔會親身出黎幫手撕埋一份？","createTime":"2019-09-20T15:38:44.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-23T09:58:41.000Z","uid":311701,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"6faa15ecdd5cf4952ab65baeafc9f97c9e114e06","tid":1583508,"uid":311701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-20T15:38:44.000Z","msg":"吹得雞叫人出黎撕，唔係自己嘆冷氣睇直播下話<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />睇死佢用念力清牆<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />佢一定出黎以身作則"},{"pid":"51bccb9a55a043edb23677f756a525262e4acde9","tid":1583508,"uid":311701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-09-20T15:40:09.000Z","msg":"答案聽日自動揭曉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"df297cb21bc6f487016856db63e41a9165401a03","tid":1583508,"uid":265221,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-20T15:40:11.000Z","msg":"肯定廿幾條友傍住佢，唔係咁易入佢中路既，葉師父<br />\n<br />\nBTW<br />\n---------------------<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">政府</span></span>借減碳排放為名，<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">要向中國買電</span></span><br />\n<br />\n「長遠減碳策略公眾參與」詻詢<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">今日截止</span></span><br />\n快啲將你既意見SEND EMAIL去：  comments@susdev.org.hk<br />\n<br />\n✏參考意見✏<br />\n<br />\n致可持續發展委員會成員：<br />\n<br />\n「長遠減碳策略公眾參與」諮詢中，當局建議以「 更緊密的區域合作」向中國購買零排放電力，然而本港電力穩定度遠高於中國南方電網，擔心向中國買電會帶來電力不穩，影響本港金融、航運、交通、以至市民日常生活。<br />\n<br />\n此外，《巴黎協定》為一些面積小、欠缺天然資源的小島嶼發展中國家(Small Island Developing States,SIDS) 如新加坡、斐濟等，可因應它們特殊情況，制訂關於溫室氣體低排放發展的策略。<br />\n由於香港地少人多，局限可再生能源發展，亦缺乏天然資源，可選擇的減排策略有限，與其他小島嶼發展中國家情況面臨同樣的挑戰。<br />\n<br />\n就此本人有以下意見：<br />\n<br />\n一. 聯網供電會損害供電穩定，故此反對進一步向中國買電，反對採取更緊密的區域合作，香港應以本地發電為主，確保電力穩定；<br />\n二. 遵照2014年未來發電燃料組合諮詢，增加本地天然氣發電及可再生能源比例，代替區域聯網；<br />\n三. 爭取香港以地區名義，直接向政府間氣候變化專門委員會(IPCC)匯報減排策略；<br />\n四. 爭取以發展中國家/地區(Small Island Developing States) 名義，因應香港的情況，以更彈性的方式履行《巴黎協定》；<br />\n五. 放緩人口增長，收緊移民政策，減低整體耗電量；<br />\n六. 制訂具體香港再工業化政策，加強本港農業及回收業的支援，減少貨物入口時的碳排放。"},{"pid":"00ead6d3bd3745729589145e7df068bddf6561f9","tid":1583508,"uid":185018,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-20T15:41:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/tyDXeBg.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FtyDXeBg.jpg&h=77800313&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n叫何妖清潔香港，自己負責"},{"pid":"a13f9e57fdb3bbccf024fa7a07ddde7677e3a18b","tid":1583508,"uid":285899,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-20T15:44:31.000Z","msg":"佢冷氣軍師來"},{"pid":"927a3cf24336e1eedf337c7263d0a43d182ad3ab","tid":1583508,"uid":311701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a13f9e57fdb3bbccf024fa7a07ddde7677e3a18b","tid":1583508,"uid":285899,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-20T15:44:31.000Z","msg":"佢冷氣軍師來"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-20T15:46:31.000Z","msg":"佢係深藍嘅黃絲<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"451e28f1b25c3d3fe0a8b0ba4c41eb9ea6138be9","tid":1583508,"uid":285899,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"927a3cf24336e1eedf337c7263d0a43d182ad3ab","tid":1583508,"uid":311701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a13f9e57fdb3bbccf024fa7a07ddde7677e3a18b","tid":1583508,"uid":285899,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-20T15:44:31.000Z","msg":"佢冷氣軍師來"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-20T15:46:31.000Z","msg":"佢係深藍嘅黃絲<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-20T15:46:59.000Z","msg":"精警 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3e257ee3c1c425d6e93614d36320e3db26e3c390","tid":1583508,"uid":127929,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"51bccb9a55a043edb23677f756a525262e4acde9","tid":1583508,"uid":311701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"ci